    ParameterizableEventInstance

    public abstract class AbstractEventInstance
extends EventImpl
    Base class to be extended by actual event instances. It extends the basic Event type by automatically setting its type (see: Event.getType()) and the timestamp it was created (see:Event.getTimestamp()).
